Sticky Sesame Chicken

6 fillets, boneless chicken thigh
5 tbsp, sweet chili sauce
5 tbsp, hoisin sauce
1 chunk, ginger
4 cloves, garlic, peeled and crushed
1 tbsp, rice vinegar
1.5 tbsp, sesame seeds
1 tbsp, soy sauce
1/2 cup, chicken stock

35 minutes, serves 4-6

In a medium bowl, whisk together chili sauce, hoisin sauce, ginger, garlic, vinegar, sesame seeds, soy sauce, and chicken stock.

Add thighs to IP and pour over the sauce mixture.

Pressure cook on HIGH for 15 minutes.

Release pressure naturally for 10 minutes, then release manually.
